docs.text: midnight cowboy presents two familiar incarnations of the american dream .

docs.text: there is the frontier fantasy that if you are brave enough to repel a few indians , you can set up a ranch out west and raise a beautiful family .

docs.text: then there is the jay gatsby dream that a man of humble stock , with perseverance , can make a fortune in the big city .
